<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="21">
<number box="[151,167,320,343]" pageId="1" pageNumber="21" value="2.0">2</number>
. Oral margin narrow in frontal view, gena almost non-existent or extremely narrow, usually only represented by a ridge between oral-genal cup and inner eye margin; eyes of males dichoptic 
<emphasis box="[1012,1338,352,375]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="21">
......................................... 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille" authorityName="Latreille" box="[1288,1338,352,375]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Usia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Usia</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
Latreille
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,224,439]" pageId="1" pageNumber="21">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="21">
